query: SELECT workspace_user.workspace_id as "workspace_id: Uuid", workspace_user.role_id as "role_id: Uuid", role_resource_permissions_exclude.permission_id as "permission_id: Uuid", role_resource_permissions_exclude.resource_id as "resource_id: Uuid" FROM role_resource_permissions_exclude JOIN workspace_user ON workspace_user.role_id = role_resource_permissions_exclude.role_id WHERE workspace_user.user_id = $1;
